Name: Sergi Roberto
Number: 20
Position: Midfielder
Goals: 12
Assists: 37

Sergi Roberto is one of the most versatile players in the squad and is known for his ability to get into the box.
When Sergi Roberto was 14 years old he traded the town of Reus for La Masia. The ex-Nàstic Tarragona midfielder 
improved year after year until he became a crucial player for Luis Enrique’s Barça B team.
